{"tid":1515784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］BNO個聯署咪撚簽","createTime":"2019-08-29T10:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T09:18:29.000Z","uid":189564,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d2f67aa070bcdc50e22d2aaed97de7bfa7ce52b0","tid":1515784,"uid":189564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:06:18.000Z","msg":"Petition<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\nPeople in Hong Kong who hold the British National (Overseas) passport are British; however, the British government is refusing and avoiding giving these Hong Kongers the<br />\n<br />\nMore details<br />\nThe Chinese government is ignoring the Sino Anglo Agreements signed in 1981. It could be a disaster if we keep ignoring this is happening. Hong Kongers will come in as political refugees. We will need a lot of effort to house them and bad for the British reputations to the International community then.<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母issac ko 呢個傻西 grammar又錯 篇野又1999 你班人仲叫人簽<br />\n<br />\n內容大致如下：bno應該要平權 因為中共ignore份聲明 所以香港人會入英國做政治難民 英國就會用大量資源去處理呢d香港政治難民 使到英國聲譽受損<br />\n<br />\n問題黎喇 中共打口炮話聲明過時無效 持bno人士無居英權所以變做大量難民湧入英國 咩邏輯 依加大鳩英國佬？bno人士憑咩可以申請做難民 仲要話人地就要用資源處理我地 1999<br />\n<br />\n搵人開過個新同埋1/9去大使館喇<br />\n<br />\n利申 繼續bno"},{"pid":"733b6aeee0074e639a2f579e92b22596d8369aec","tid":1515784,"uid":189564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:07:41.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"5e8d6a50765f9f2de9c43f8739997f0c74d0852c","tid":1515784,"uid":189564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:07:54.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"77cd2a253deff0ddf2ba44003fbe8143f136c6be","tid":1515784,"uid":189564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:08:04.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"ffcf6285a275d82636b0ecd61d559b15bedbad62","tid":1515784,"uid":189564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:08:16.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"14f128ba225b616725441f65